Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛 為什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你为什么要做恶忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答案…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就在那里告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女的地图…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.63,0:00:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我等着你 雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.35,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要躲了 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被发现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是老师啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我应该是叫你们在房间里面待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为老师神色有些反常所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弄清蛇女的位置了么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恐怕是了
