Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:10.14,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:29.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:34.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}暗雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:39.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:50.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:57.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:03.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.94,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.31,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.86,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:16.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:21.53,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON'T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:29.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:10.14,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.94,0:01:29.36,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:34.45,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:39.75,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:42.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:44.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:50.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:57.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:03.02,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.94,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:08.31,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.86,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:16.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:21.53,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
